  "description": "<div>\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: #006400;\">今日知识点--authorized 与 unauthorized&nbsp;</span></strong></div>\n<div>\n\t<img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/10/07/010b35fcf9350c18e12110900706e74a.png\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 436px;\" /></div>\n<div>\n\tauthorize&nbsp;的意思是&ldquo;批准&rdquo;、&ldquo;授权&rdquo;，在谈到职务权力的时候通常都会谈到它：</div>\n<div>\n\tYour position doesn't have the right to&nbsp;authorize&nbsp;this.你的职位无权批准这个。</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t它的形容词形式以及其反义词也很常见，并且经常出现在专业名词之中：</div>\n<div>\n\tauthorized agent全权代理人<br />\n\tauthorized bank制定银行<br />\n\tauthorized dealer特许经营商</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t其反义词就是在前面加&nbsp;un&nbsp;变成&nbsp;unauthorized</div>\n<div>\n\t它的名词形式是&nbsp;authority，可以翻译为&ldquo;权力&rdquo;、&ldquo;权威性&rdquo;：</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\tFortunately, I'm the one who has the&nbsp;authority&nbsp;to do this.幸运的是，我就是那个有权干这个的人。</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\tI think your children are starting to doubt your&nbsp;authority.我觉得你的孩子已经开始质疑你的权威性了。</div>\n<div>\n\t<img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/10/07/725573a60bd15eb841fb9e430f3d5be8.png\" /></div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1215701/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1215701\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1207801/\">如何一个人练口语？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1215102/\">心理学：一杯星巴克几十块，真的值得吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1213540/\">Quora精选：生活中的英国女王是什么样？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1212326/\">如何应对消极情绪？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2